Nigeria Economic and Financial Crimes Commissions Arrests Top Politician

-- B y   V i n c e n t   N w a n m a
-- 
2011-06-06T06:32:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/nigeria-economic-and-financial-crimes-commissions-arrests-top-politician.html
Nigeria’s Economic and Financial
Crimes Commissions arrested Dimeji Bankole, speaker of the  House
of Representatives  yesterday for “various allegations of
corruption,”  Femi Babafemi , spokesman for the agency said by
phone from Abuja today.  Bankole will be interrogated for “two or three days,”
Babafemi said. “From our office, he will be charged to court,”
he added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Nwanma in Lagos at 
 vnwanma@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Agnes Nikoi at 
 anikoi@bloomberg.net  